<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n03021b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n03" href="#n03021b">N03 (VI.B.3)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n03all.htm#n03021b"> 21(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Tu azzurro hai l&apos;occhio / ecc </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: This is taken from the aria &lsquo;Recondita armonia&rdquo; in Act 1 of Puccini&apos;s <i>Tosca</i>, in which the painter Cavoradossi compares the features of the woman in the portrait he is painting with those of Tosca: <i>E te, beltade ignota, / cinta di chiome bionde! / Tu azzurro hai l&apos;occhio, / Tosca ha l&apos;occhio nero!</i> (And you, unknown fair-haired beauty, have blue eyes &mdash;Tosca&apos;s are black!). &lsquo;ecc&rsquo; is an abbreviation of It. <i>eccetera</i>: et cetera. </mm> </dd></dl>
